         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Decr. 31st 1881. ¶ Alice Springs. ¶ My dear Baron. ¶  ¶ By this mail I have much pleasure in sending you a leaf &amp; two specimens of fruit of the Dwarf Palm. The leaf is a small one but I presume it wil...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">81.12.31</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Ernest Flint</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M1, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS found with a specimen of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Macrozamia macdonnellii</seg> (MEL 237354), collected by E. Flint at Alice Springs in December 1881. MS annotation by M: 'Answ 4/2/82'. Letter not found.</p>
               </note>Decr. 31st 1881.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">Alice Springs.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Baron.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>By this mail I have much pleasure in sending you a leaf &amp; two specimens of fruit of the Dwarf Palm. The leaf is a small one but I presume it will answer your purpose the average length of leaves is from 3 ft 6 in to 4 ft 6 in.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I trust the parcel will come safely to hand &amp; will be of use to you.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wishing you the Compts of the Season &amp; assuring you that at any future time that I can assist you my services are at your disposal</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">I am</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>my dear Baron</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Very Faithfully yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ernest E S Flint</p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
